# Shopify ETL Example

Data Loom HQ was used to sanitize the Shopify 2025 dataset before SQL benchmarking.

> “Utilized my custom ETL application, Data Loom HQ, to sanitize and organize the raw Kaggle data before conducting the final analysis.”

Key steps:
- Removed duplicates  
- Standardized price ranges  
- Normalized numeric fields  
- Cleaned text fields  
- Prepared dataset for BigQuery ingestion  
